song.title: Worldwide Slack
song.info:
Worldwide slack .. chuck biscuits % kosmic ..
Here's a trancy house/acid track that i hope some of you'll enjoy...
Samples are from 808 state, soundwave's x5 pad library, force format (anyoona bass) and my own sample library.
Greetings go to vivid, soundwave, maral, malcolm and basehead
If you'd like to use any of my samples from this track, then please at least let me know about it, thanks. Thanks to starchild for the song title.
